name: Henbane Farms
description:
• Walk left/right with [A]/[D] or left/right arrow keys
  • Hold [Shift] to run. This is important because you have limited time.
  • Hit [Spacebar] or [Enter] to pick a crop off the ground, and to talk to someone!
  • Click the [give] button on screen or press [G] when talking to someone to give them your crop.

Thanks for playing!
